caption.title: Analysis of variance of the effects of OA and T and their interaction on the absolute flows of contributing functional groups from trophic levels 2 to 3.
caption.p: Functional groups were ordered in terms of their contribution to total energy flows. Significant differences are indicated with asterisks, with *: p < 0.05, **: p < 0.01, and ***: p < 0.001. OA, elevated CO 2; T, elevated temperature.
